<section>
<title>Detailed Description</title>

<para>Manages the position and orientation of the bones in a model rigged for skeletal animation. </para>



<para>The class expects that the graphics model&apos;s bones that correspond to the bones in the <link linkend="_namespace_leap_1_1_unity_1_1_leap">Leap</link> Motion hand model are in the same order in the bones array. </para>
